dct_title_s: Kents restaurant in Atlantic City map, verso
dct_description_sm: Reverse of street map highlighting Kents Restaurant. The verso is actually the outside cover of a tri-fold brochure format map sponsored by Kents Restaurants which had several locations in Atlantic City during the early 20th Century. This side features the title masthead, an alphabetic street index and an advertisement for Kents.
